sections.text:
54-179.03.Electronic inspection, defined.

Electronic inspection means a method of performing inspections of livestock enrolled with the Nebraska Brand Committee utilizing approved nonvisual identifier means of identification.

SourceLaws 2021, LB572, ยง 6.
